ion">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="G-Gnoll-Hypothesis"><a href="#G-Gnoll-Hypothesis" class="headerlink" title="G - Gnoll Hypothesis"></a><a href="https://open.kattis.com/problems/gnollhypothesis">G - Gnoll Hypothesis</a></h2></li><li><p>题意：怪物池中有 $n$ 只怪物，每只怪物的生成概率为 $p_i$  。现在怪物池中的怪物只有 $k$ 只会生成（任意 $k$ 只），不生成的怪物原本的生成概率将会向后转移给下一只会可能生成的怪物（如果最后的怪物不会生成，那么概率会转移给第一只可能生成的）。求所有怪物现在的生成概率。</p></li><li><p>思路：核心在于概率的合并，对于第 $i$ 只怪物，如果 $p_{i-j}$ 要合并到 $p_i$ ，那么区间 $[i-j, i]$ 之间一定是不能生成的怪物，即需要在剩余的 $n - j - 1$ 个怪物中选择 $k-1$ 个怪物。因此计算 $p_i^{‘}$ 的公式为： $p_i^{‘} = \sum_{j=0}^{n-k} p_{i-j}·\frac{C_{n-j-1}^{k-1}}{C_n^k}$ 。</p><pre class="line-numbers language-cpp" data-language="cpp"><code class="language-cpp"><span class="token macro property"><span class="token directive-hash">#</span><span class="token directive keyword">include</span> <span class="token string">&lt;algorithm></span></span><span class="token macro property"><span class="token directive-hash">#</span><span class="token directive keyword">include</span> <span class="token string">&lt;bitset></span></span><span class="token macro property"><span class="token directive-hash">#</span><span class="token directive keyword">include</span> <span class="token string">&lt;cmath></span></span><span class="token macro property"><span class=